HEADWORD: Oh
<hw>Oh</hw> <pr>(⟦omac⟧)</pr>, <pos>interj.</pos> <ety>[See <er>O</er>,
<pos>interj.</pos>]</ety> <def>An exclamation expressing various
emotions, according to the tone and manner, especially surprise, pain,
sorrow, anxiety, or a wish. See the Note under <er>O</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

